Q1. Show top 5 laptop brands by median Price

In[60]:
a = (
    df.groupby(by = "brand")
    .agg({"Price": "median"})
    .nlargest(5, "Price")
    .round(2)
)

Show bottom 3 laptop brands by average Price for Touchscreen laptops

In[66]:
b = (
    df.query("Touchscreen == 'Yes'")
    .groupby(by = "brand")
    .agg({"Price": "mean"})
    .nsmallest(3, "Price")
    .round(2)
)
